[
    {
        "text": "There may come a time when you want to send an email to multiple people at once,...",
        "startTime": 447,
        "endTime": 3883,
        "slowStartTime": 820,
        "slowEndTime": 6050
    },
    {
        "text": "...at which point you may wish to make use of the CC feature.",
        "startTime": 4268,
        "endTime": 7361,
        "slowStartTime": 6552,
        "slowEndTime": 11266
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, if you take one thing away from this talk, let it be the CC rule.",
        "startTime": 8297,
        "endTime": 14021,
        "slowStartTime": 12595,
        "slowEndTime": 21257
    },
    {
        "text": "The CC rule states that primary recipients of an email,...",
        "startTime": 15547,
        "endTime": 19923,
        "slowStartTime": 23470,
        "slowEndTime": 30109
    },
    {
        "text": "...who are expected to respond, should go in the \"To\" field.",
        "startTime": 20307,
        "endTime": 23965,
        "slowStartTime": 30610,
        "slowEndTime": 36172
    },
    {
        "text": "Other recipients of an email, who are not expected to respond...",
        "startTime": 25046,
        "endTime": 28956,
        "slowStartTime": 37719,
        "slowEndTime": 43659
    },
    {
        "text": "...and who are included as a courtesy or for their information,...",
        "startTime": 29281,
        "endTime": 32734,
        "slowStartTime": 44072,
        "slowEndTime": 49326
    },
    {
        "text": "...should go in the \"CC\" field.",
        "startTime": 33065,
        "endTime": 35152,
        "slowStartTime": 49747,
        "slowEndTime": 52953
    },
    {
        "text": "Next time you receive an email that's been addressed to multiple people, take a look:...",
        "startTime": 36179,
        "endTime": 40223,
        "slowStartTime": 54419,
        "slowEndTime": 60560
    },
    {
        "text": "...Are you a primary recipient, or are you on CC?",
        "startTime": 40311,
        "endTime": 44039,
        "slowStartTime": 60616,
        "slowEndTime": 66284
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you need to respond?",
        "startTime": 44248,
        "endTime": 45575,
        "slowStartTime": 66522,
        "slowEndTime": 68587
    },
    {
        "text": "What I love about the CC rule is it makes the expectations on your recipients so clear.",
        "startTime": 46747,
        "endTime": 53809,
        "slowStartTime": 70271,
        "slowEndTime": 80938
    },
    {
        "text": "If you're in the \"To\" field, you should respond;...",
        "startTime": 54205,
        "endTime": 56951,
        "slowStartTime": 81457,
        "slowEndTime": 85652
    },
    {
        "text": "...if you're on the \"CC\" field, you should not respond.",
        "startTime": 57276,
        "endTime": 59981,
        "slowStartTime": 86064,
        "slowEndTime": 90197
    },
    {
        "text": "And it also reduces the burden of email by hopefully cutting back on the number of emails sent.",
        "startTime": 60615,
        "endTime": 66959,
        "slowStartTime": 91072,
        "slowEndTime": 100663
    },
    {
        "text": "Those people on CC don't have that awkward moment where they're wondering,...",
        "startTime": 67277,
        "endTime": 70924,
        "slowStartTime": 101066,
        "slowEndTime": 106611
    },
    {
        "text": "...\"Am I expected to pitch in here?\"",
        "startTime": 71386,
        "endTime": 73465,
        "slowStartTime": 107229,
        "slowEndTime": 110422
    },
    {
        "text": "The CC rule will change your email life.",
        "startTime": 74108,
        "endTime": 76745,
        "slowStartTime": 111312,
        "slowEndTime": 115342
    }
]